🌟 Welcome to Pytalon! 🌟

This project was built with one goal in mind — to make learning Python feel less like a chore and more like a conversation.

You are free to use, share, and build upon this software.
Whether you're a curious beginner taking your first steps in Python, or an experienced developer who wants to contribute something great — this license is here to empower you, not stand in your way.

