💙 A note from the creator:

Pytalon started as a simple idea — what if learning Python felt like talking to a friend instead of reading a textbook?

If this project helped you write your first line of code, understand a concept that once confused you, or inspired you to build something of your own — that's everything.

Keep building. Keep sharing. Keep learning.
And if Pytalon made your journey a little easier, a ⭐ on GitHub means the world.

Together, we make coding friendlier for everyone. 🐍✨
